data.value: Dr. (Col) MS Sandhu was the Senior Consultant (Hon) - Interventional Cardiology at Batra Hospital and Medical Research Center, New Delhi before joining Artemis. He had a distinguished career in the Army Medical Corps and was last posted as Senior Adviser (Medicine and Cardiology) at Base Hospital, DelhiCantt andwas also holding appointment of Addl. Professor of Medicine andCardiology atArmy College of Medical Sciences, Delhi Cantt.
